entries.s_43: I am doing important work, but I could use some help. Down below, do you see that bunker? Some Drall terrorists are using it as they plan their future crimes. I mean to stop them, but I need to know what they are planning. Could you enter their bunker and find out? The information I seek can be downloaded from their data terminals.
entries.s_47: I understand. I should not have asked.
entries.s_48: Thank you. This information will be crucial to stopping them before they can harm innocent people.
entries.s_49: You will find information about their plans in their data terminals.
